        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>The transmission oil cooler mounting bracket on 2500 and 2600 Models built between June 28, 1994,
                    and February 23, 1995, with Cummins L10 and M11 engines and Allison automatic transmissions may
                    fail. If the transmission oil cooler mount fails, a sudden loss of engine coolant may result which
                    could cause serious engine damage.
                </para>
                <para>This Authorized Field Change contains parts and service information to replace the transmission
                    oil cooler mounting bracket.
                </para>
                <para></para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
